{"tid":385262,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真post][好撚mean] 唐氏綜合症病人算唔算正常人","createTime":"2017-09-03T05:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T17:13:32.000Z","uid":136116,"like":13,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8a62956e33aa9067335aa7b0326bd194c0fa6642","tid":385262,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"首先講明呢個post 冇意冒犯任何人, 純粹想做下學術探討, 究竟唐氏綜合症病人係生物, 道德, 社會學觀點嚟睇屬唔屬於正常人(人類)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算, 因為佢地係由兩個正常人類交配而生, 而且道德上唔當佢地正常人係一件好過份嘅事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔算, 人類有46條染色體, 但係唐氏綜合症病人有47條, 所以佢地生物學上唔算同我地同一物種<br />\n<br />\n有其他理據不妨講下, 大家討論一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d822122b8f654be7d3e3fcadc0ba54697fb8de90","tid":385262,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"討論目的/意義？"},{"pid":"3bd98bffdfe304fc9470cfcc32dd2bee2cac9f05","tid":385262,"uid":9732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"正常即係大多數，所以唔算？"},{"pid":"435dbcdcf2ed5665ebb95f6f574ce3ffd3af1757","tid":385262,"uid":136116,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"依家上學術台討論原來要講意義, 大家互相交流下思想都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1c362a778970461f2cc318387ee9efe13ba2f5","tid":385262,"uid":52276,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:41:19.000Z","msg":"你都識講有病啦&hellip;仲叫正常？"},{"pid":"1e88deb1365aac0b724ad918f36e1441ea664cf0","tid":385262,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都識講有病啦&hellip;仲叫正常？</blockquote><br />\nSorry 我可能講得唔太清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我指嘅係應唔應該當佢地係生物學上所指嘅 「人類」"},{"pid":"48edb9ba86d47523a636d40cfbafe94ab10b82b9","tid":385262,"uid":1374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>討論目的/意義？</blockquote><br />\n你上高登/連登開post又有咩意義 ？"},{"pid":"f3dc82e939082e76c7bfe6b5f039f9488a5a710c","tid":385262,"uid":106967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你都識講有病啦&hellip;仲叫正常？</blockquote><br />\nSorry 我可能講得唔太清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我指嘅係應唔應該當佢地係生物學上所指嘅 「人類」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6337988ab62c3fbf817fd1ea46c221896483d4bd","tid":385262,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"認真post 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307849162aed3dadab130f4b7c0e300bcaa9f47f","tid":385262,"uid":22310,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家上學術台討論原來要講意義, 大家互相交流下思想都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係正常又會點唔正常又會點<br />\n遺傳學角度你當mutant 就唔正常<br />\n但如果社會上係當佢係有病嘅正常人<br />\nBtw 討論意義好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係一味拋哂所有角度出嚟算<br />\n意義例如<br />\n要諗down syndrome 病人有冇人權咁未要諗佢算唔算人"},{"pid":"e6b88e3babe299cdf2959de71f31a73e3b281e7a","tid":385262,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"唔使起哂龬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf26007cd881ea587f0abb0fe6bccb677829251","tid":385262,"uid":59465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:51:22.000Z","msg":"樓主 連基本邏輯都未搞好<br />\n兩個chooses入邊無 唐氏綜合症病人同我地係同一物種但係唔正常<br />\n<br />\n但係個標題又問人佢哋係唔係正常人<br />\n做乜鳩"},{"pid":"62db4bafcabd26019ae50201407d7e2bc4c0b5ce","tid":385262,"uid":136116,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家上學術台討論原來要講意義, 大家互相交流下思想都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係正常又會點唔正常又會點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">遺傳學角度你當mutant 就唔正常</span><br />\n但如果社會上係當佢係有病嘅正常人<br />\nBtw 討論意義好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係一味拋哂所有角度出嚟算<br />\n意義例如<br />\n要諗down syndrome 病人有冇人權咁未要諗佢算唔算人</blockquote><br />\n但係唔係所有有遺傳病嘅人都會唔符合生物學上對人類嘅定義喎<br />\n好似力克胡哲咁, 雖然因為遺傳病冇手冇腳, 但係係生物學定義上佢都係人類喎<br />\n<br />\n純粹其實覺得想係唔同方面睇吓down syndrome 嘅人應該點樣classify 姐<br />\n可以係 道德(人權上)係人, 生物學方面唔係 咁樣<br />\n<br />\nAnyway 多謝巴打參與討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bea4e264e8d902bd69c59ff717542cc9f8965d","tid":385262,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:53:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主 連基本邏輯都未搞好<br />\n兩個chooses入邊無 唐氏綜合症病人同我地係同一物種但係唔正常<br />\n<br />\n但係個標題又問人佢哋係唔係正常人<br />\n做乜鳩</blockquote><br />\nSorry 我打錯標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdffbc7aa1cef983aa52d7353abfb5dccb66dfec","tid":385262,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:56:50.000Z","msg":"標題更正 : 算唔算係同生物學所定義的人類同一物種"},{"pid":"5dc13a64395e412142d721b2e7db5e91a49745d4","tid":385262,"uid":89146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:14:13.000Z","msg":"咁白老虎仲係咪老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b306ef29cf09f90873aecd1174aa7b9aece0710","tid":385262,"uid":111990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都識講有病啦&hellip;仲叫正常？</blockquote><br />\n有病就唔正常架啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你感冒發燒係咪都唔係正常人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6794b0f2a86a23d9c188a42de43e8ae86b3b4776","tid":385262,"uid":76885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"生物學上 物種 Species既定義<br />\n<br />\n兩個生物能夠生出有生育能力既後代 兩個生物就係同Species"},{"pid":"c8e3c28033e1aae61c8ed29950c713d0204fc3bc","tid":385262,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"睇你點定義<br />\n柒色體突變左你可以話佢唔係&quot;正常&quot;人"},{"pid":"11ddbe392d61614614070809fdfec2369b5cdcd0","tid":385262,"uid":76885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"道德上<br />\n假設佢地唔係正常人<br />\n咁又點?<br />\n佢地無基本Human right? <br />\n<br />\n個問題好似去返<br />\n正常人既意思係咩<br />\n你認為既正常人既意思係咩"},{"pid":"d3c74d5c0a2d0cae83474b6125c11e79cea72c53","tid":385262,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生物學上 物種 Species既定義<br />\n<br />\n兩個生物能夠生出有生育能力既後代 兩個生物就係同Species</blockquote><br />\n咁所以Down Syndrome 嘅人生物學上就唔係人類? 我都係咁睇, 同埋染色體數量有分別"},{"pid":"bba20c4ba84dcdbdc8eae2223dc7c35f79dd0a13","tid":385262,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>道德上<br />\n假設佢地唔係正常人<br />\n咁又點?<br />\n佢地無基本Human right? <br />\n<br />\n個問題好似去返<br />\n正常人既意思係咩<br />\n你認為既正常人既意思係咩</blockquote><br />\n其實佢地係社會上都享有好多權利, 但係唔知可唔可以叫做 人權"},{"pid":"9ee5cbd6d2db121f3c460f3fd20a20fdb0150ea1","tid":385262,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2ed33a89451ab80427e1dae505e232e5c77e857b","tid":385262,"uid":132295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:20:44.000Z","msg":"If a person with Down syndrome can reproduce fertile offspring with normal person, they are considered the same species <br />\n唔知有無實例"},{"pid":"23a19d380fe85f6e5ed45cbfae